Say '''Leon''' et - ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Iloilo]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 47,522 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 140.2 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumadwa ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5026.	
															
